cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.SY. 

The paper proposes an algorithm for imitation learning from observation using visual demonstrations and proprioceptive information. This involves machine learning (cs.LG) techniques for policy learning, computer vision (cs.CV) for processing visual demonstrations, robotics (cs.RO) for testing the algorithm on MuJoCo domains, artificial intelligence (cs.AI) for developing the algorithm, and systems and control (cs.SY) for leveraging proprioception in the learning process.
